import React from 'react'
import { Container } from '../Header/styles'
import { Card, Icon, User } from './style'

function TopSection() {
    return (
        <Container className = 'container'>
            <Card>
                <User>
                    <Icon>

                    </Icon>
                    <Label>
                        @nathanf
                    </Label>
                </User>
            </Card>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default TopSection
